io.github.prolobjectlink.db

Enum OperationType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<OperationType>
      • io.github.prolobjectlink.db.OperationType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<OperationType>

    public enum OperationType
extends Enum<OperationType>
    Operation code type to be interpreted by the remote server when this received a request. Support all database operations and the additional no operation (NOOP) operation type. NOOP is use when the active request is initialized and replaced when another operation type is send to server.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jose Zalacain
